tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE robotic_arm_sensor_data (
    sensor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    sensor_reading FLOAT,
    arm_position_x FLOAT,
    arm_position_y FLOAT,
    arm_position_z FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE robotic_arm_sensor_data (
  sensor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  position_x FLOAT,
  position_y FLOAT,
  position_z FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE arm_calibration (
  calibration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  sensor_id UUID,
  angle INT,
  torque FLOAT,
  duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE robotic_arm_movements (
    movement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    arm_id INT,
    movement_type VARCHAR(50),
    movement_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE robotic_arm_movements (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,
  arm_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  movement_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  movement_intensity INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE arm_positions (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,
  position_x FLOAT NOT NULL,
  position_y FLOAT NOT NULL,
  position_z FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE movement_history (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,
  from_position VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  to_position VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  duration INT NOT NULL
);
